title: Geer & Goor: Effe Geen Gent Te Makken
overview: Geer & Goor go out with a group of elderly people. They are loaded into the bus and leave the direction of Amersfoort Zoo. They entertain their guests in their own way: with a lot of crap, but also full understanding of the loneliness experienced by many elderly people. They love the ladies and gentlemen to entertain a day.
